parameters: Sheesh, what do I do, what can I even find here?
Isn't the beach like a big junkyard?
(I think, at least the ones in the city are...)
We can hang out for a while!
I've lived here for a long time and never knew that.
So what do you like to do when you're not studying?
I actually sell fishing and swimming gear and equipment!
Finally, a place where I can get swimming and fishing gear and equipment!
Wait, so do you have parents here?
I was very lucky to be invited here,
it's pretty hard to get enrolled,
you usually need some sort of special talent to get in.
Well, I guess you'd already know that!
(I thought I was enrolled because it's close to \C[20]Auntie Daisy\C[0]'s??)
(...unless I have a hidden talent I haven't discovered yet...)
Oh yes, of course, I know..! Haha...
So, \n[1]... What do you think of the ocean?
Maybe a little terrifyingly mysterious, but otherwise, super cool!
Let's hit the beach then! We can catch some fish!
Oh uh, I don't have a swimsuit with me.
Oh, I think I have some underwear you can use!
Wait for me here, I need to change my clothes.
It sure is! That's why I love diving myself into sea.
Too bad, I wasn't more useful catching fish.
Haha, it's alright! It was your first time!
The fish is cooked, take a bite.
Your cooking skill is so good, \C[12]Nina\C[0]!!
It's only salt, pepper, and some herbs.
Hey, there's a boat out there!
Has that been there this whole time?
I got it so I can get to the sea for better fishing and to find cool oceanic materials.
It's kinda dangerous to be going out alone, so I've never actually used it.
Woah, that sounds kinda cool, I'm down to go!
Well, you're gonna need some diving equipment,
and lucky for you, I sell everything you need!
Isn't that like a diving monopoly?
I said let's get to diving already!
(If I want to go to the beach then I have to buy the necessary equipments from \C[12]Nina\C[0],
it's better to save some money.)
\c[1]Can ask to go out by using Phone Call\c[0]
I'm a bit tired, I'm not thinking about diving right now...
You don't have the necessary diving equipment yet.
Wait for me here, I need to change my clothes.
I just finished changing my clothes.
It sure is! That's why I love diving myself into sea.
How did you catch it? We didn't even go that far out to sea!
You'll get better at catching, don't worry!
The fish is cooked, take a bite.
There are still a lot, eat as much as you can.
The total number of seashells is \c[1]\v[311]\c[0]!
You better take a shower or you're going to feel very unpleasant.
Thank god! You should be careful next time!
You've lost all the sea shells
I feel something strange in my pants...
My guess is you got stung by a jellyfish.
Don't worry, all you have to do is pee on it!
(I don't feel any pain, I feel something different instead... )
Thanks for the piss, I guess...
Hah! Look at my dick it's so colorful now!
You better go to a doctor and check it out.
Proceed with Kate's story to access it.\c[0]
We came to do some diving and just chill at the beach.
Come on, it will be fun!
I never get tired of this.
Hehe, you're always so scared of everything.
Well kinda, but I like it!
And this is just the start.
I got lots of things planned for later!
Yeah yeah, I'm gonna go start my sandcastle now!
Let's see who's got the best sandcastle!
I went diving for some fish as usual.
As soon as I dive in,
there was a freaking squid right in front of my face.
I caught that thing and had me some fried squid!
I wish I could do that.
I was swimming near a coral reef, minding my own business
Next thing I know, I spotted a shark.
You mustve bolted out of there!
Nope. I kept my cool, swam to the side,
Id be halfway back to shore!
I wish I could do that.
One day, I was free diving.
this huge manta ray glides right over me.
Yeah, it was. I swam alongside it for a bit,
then watched it disappear into the blue.
I wish I couldve seen that!
You put yourself out there today and showed everyone your skills.
I feel pretty good about today,
and I have you guys to thank.
I know I'm usually pretty shy and quiet,
but you guys brought me out of my shell and I got to try new things because of it.
Hey! Lets eat, the fish is ready!
I could eat this every day.
I had the same reaction when I tried it,
Going to the beach is the best!!
Hey! Its nearby, we can go here anytime we like.
Hey! Slow down, theres still a lot left.
Hang out with \C[21]Zoe\c[0] and \C[4]Felix\c[0] has been unlocked!
\c[1]Can ask to go out by using Phone Call\c[0]
